{"id":"99350549-e7d3-4bf7-8c72-9a78eb5ca474","name":"Evi | BYSTANDER","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 29, 79);\"><strong>| MODERN FANTASY |</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wqh9GKAtZzo&amp;list=RDwqh9GKAtZzo&amp;start_radio=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 29, 79);\"><strong>▶︎•၊၊||၊|။||||။၊|။•</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 29, 79);\"><strong>CW: VIOLENCE, DEATH, HEAVY GORE, WAR</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 29, 79);\"><strong>Paramedic {{char}}</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>Set in the Modern Fantasy universe created by </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/aacc6328-14d2-4d53-b6d4-0e5c3b934884_profile-of-reinborld\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>@Reinborld</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>Character art by </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fen%2Fusers%2F3205297\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\">@</span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"sc-8f427104-6 bZVGlc\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fen%2Fusers%2F3205297\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>HAGURUMA-C</strong></span></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>MAIN SCENARIO</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>New year's eve just ended. The festive season still lingers in the cold weather. For Evi, this was just another night of duty, maybe a night spent in the EMS bay. However... things fell into disarray as power was immediately cut off. Hundreds of calls overwhelmed hospitals.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>Evi was dispatched to an emergency call. On the way, chaos erupted in the streets as gas started to spread, choking civilians. Bangs echoed from far away, not fireworks, but gunshots.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>This wasn't just a power outage, this was a systematic attack.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>POSSIBLE USER ROLES:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>- A civilian helping Evi out</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>- Emergency Services(police, firefighter, a fellow paramedic)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>- SWAT units trying to enforce order amid the chaos</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>- Stationed UN soldier</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>- SC soldier part of the attack</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>______________________________________________________________</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>2ND SCENARIO</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><em>Takes place a few days before the main scenario. Evi just brought in a patient from a car crash and contemplates her life in the hospital cafeteria. A calmer start.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>POSSIBLE USER ROLES:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 243, 230);\"><strong>- </strong><em>A patient in the hospital(some wounded UN soldier or some shi)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"WW5BM8bB3_sUgOvzU9pTP.webp","creator":"temto","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":2817,"messages":46306,"created_at":"2025-12-01T05:53:06.949817+00:00"}